# Moodle plugin paths → separate git repos (submodule layout).
# Format: relative_path|clone_url|branch
# Lines starting with # are ignored. Branch defaults to main if empty; submodulize/unsubmodulize
# fall back to the remote default branch when that branch does not exist (e.g. master-only repos).
#
# Synced from repo CSV: Evaluation of LSU moodle messy plugins(List) (3).csv
# Custom URL preferred over third-party when both are set.
# How to refresh from CSV and team policy: cleandev/TEAM-PROCESS.md
#
# --- One repo per path (compatible with submodulize.sh / unsubmodulize.sh) ---

